A DAD who prepared lunch for his five kids is heartbroken
after two of them died, allegedly from accidental food poisoning.According to Daily
Nation, Peter Onyango Olanga from Siaya County cooked lunch for his kids
last Sunday. His wife, Seline Onyango, had been attending a funeral at a
village about an hour’s drive away.Peter prepared cassava for the kids, aged between one and
11, and they ate at about 1pm. But at 7pm, all hell broke loose as all of them
